  "title": "[Urgent!] Waiter/ Waitress/ Waitperson - 4.5 Days Work/ Central",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li>Location : Central</li><li>4.5 Days Work</li><li>Young and energetic environment</li><li>Annual Increment</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Welcomed and seated guests courteously, ensuring a friendly and professional dining experience.</li><li><p>Accurately took food and beverage orders and entered them into the POS system in a timely manner.</p></li><li><p>Served food and beverages efficiently while maintaining quality, presentation, and customer satisfaction.</p></li><li><p>Maintained cleanliness and readiness of tables, dining areas, and workstations in accordance with hygiene standards.</p></li><li><p>Addressed guest inquiries and provided menu recommendations to enhance the overall dining experience.</p></li><li>Coordinated closely with kitchen and service teams, and assisted with opening, closing, and operational duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate with relevant experience are welcome to apply</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>To Apply, kindly click on the <strong>\"APPLY NOW\"</strong> button</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Staffking Pte Ltd (20C0358) | Boo Seng Hong (R25129172)</p>",
